{"tid":1358631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［727］戰略 不燒村不拆祠堂","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:38:09.000Z","uid":48521,"like":226,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"58a1905e6db094a36f5bd6c88a3c3ba67cdbc9ca","tid":1358631,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"以正視聽<br />\n<br />\n727不燒村不拆祠堂<br />\n<br />\n不主動進攻圍村 只被動勇武<br />\n<br />\n反對鄉黑 警黑 相互勾結<br />\n向閂閘警署 聲討警黑責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5595d374ba8c4a0ea9de9890ffce11a69bb9ba3a","tid":1358631,"uid":234202,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727反鄉黑行動<br />\n和理優 但會還手</span></span>"},{"pid":"8fd187a57ed4c356788bd0f6e308c1521cd54674","tid":1358631,"uid":164938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:30:42.000Z","msg":"7.27元朗見<br />\n有巴打話3點太遲 麻煩可唔可以send最update圖比我？<br />\n我想幫手做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbCwESw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbCwESw.png&h=57e30dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXsc8LS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXsc8LS.png&h=72624af5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLnQaZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLnQaZc.png&h=1a1599df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30fc81cdf3d1535787762d92496fd1a5a10fae78","tid":1358631,"uid":251414,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97d6860dc8cca4f04b052ff53d